summary: Completed comprehensive testing of HabitMap application. All backend APIs are functioning correctly (18/18 tests passed). Frontend testing successful with all core features working: authentication, habit management, mood logging, AI insights generation, settings, and dashboard heatmap visualization. The app demonstrates excellent integration between frontend and backend with proper JWT authentication, real-time data updates, and responsive UI design.
passed_tests: Create, edit, and delete habits with color selection
Mark habits as done/not done for each day
Heatmap calendar visualization showing 30-day habit completion
Mood logging with emoji selector and note
Calendar integration for mood date selection
Dashboard showing all habit heatmaps and mood timeline
AI-powered insights generation using GPT-5 (correlating habits with mood)
Analytics summary showing total habits, completions, and average mood
Settings page with theme toggle (light/dark) and color palette selection
Real-time data updates and state management
